@startuml
[*] --> OffState
OffState --> AlarmActivated : set alarm time
AlarmActivated --> AlarmActive : activate alarm
AlarmActive --> AlarmStopped : stop alarm
AlarmActive --> Ringing : current time matches set alarm time
Ringing --> AlarmStopped : stop alarm
AlarmStopped --> AlarmActivated : next scheduled alarm time

@enduml
